{"tid":2058642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局官員上班看A片打手槍挨罰3000","createTime":"2020-06-10T10:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T14:43:48.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6baf578ce970dd931f6bb70cce8752df91cbdd","tid":2058642,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">台北</span>市政府黃姓教育官員借調教師研習中心期間，在研習中心圖書室看A片、打手槍，遭依公然猥褻罪起訴。台北地院審理期間，黃男認罪協商，法官今判罰3000元，得易服勞役3天，不得上訴。<br />\n <br />\n檢方調查，黃男擔任北市某小學行政專員，借調到台北市教師研習中心工作時，於2018年2月3日上午10時許，在圖書室使用私人筆記型電腦觀賞A片，並當場打手槍。<br />\n <br />\n黃男另還使用公用電腦上色情網站，觀賞《強暴美麗巨乳妹》、《Toyko-Hot陰部異常玩弄》、《初次體驗酒店小姐》等A片，有同事看不下去，調閱監視器向政風處檢舉，因而遭移送法辦。<br />\n <br />\n檢方偵查期間，黃男只承認看A片，否認打手槍，但因過程全被監視器錄下，檢察官不採信黃的辯詞，仍依公然猥褻罪將他起訴。北院審理時，黃男一改先前態度，與檢察官認罪協商，法官最後判罰3000元，得易服勞役3天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200610004118-260402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200610004118-260402&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=caa7e87c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200610004118-260402</a>"},{"pid":"0e233e296c0847aedf10554a9baaa1d92a9bb115","tid":2058642,"uid":148002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:22:12.000Z","msg":"台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5798cd07e350cbaadff2adff124cf093f2047478","tid":2058642,"uid":103645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f6baf578ce970dd931f6bb70cce8752df91cbdd","tid":2058642,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">台北</span>市政府黃姓教育官員借調教師研習中心期間，在研習中心圖書室看A片、打手槍，遭依公然猥褻罪起訴。台北地院審理期間，黃男認罪協商，法官今判罰3000元，得易服勞役3天，不得上訴。<br />\n <br />\n檢方調查，黃男擔任北市某小學行政專員，借調到台北市教師研習中心工作時，於2018年2月3日上午10時許，在圖書室使用私人筆記型電腦觀賞A片，並當場打手槍。<br />\n <br />\n黃男另還使用公用電腦上色情網站，觀賞《強暴美麗巨乳妹》、《Toyko-Hot陰部異常玩弄》、《初次體驗酒店小姐》等A片，有同事看不下去，調閱監視器向政風處檢舉，因而遭移送法辦。<br />\n <br />\n檢方偵查期間，黃男只承認看A片，否認打手槍，但因過程全被監視器錄下，檢察官不採信黃的辯詞，仍依公然猥褻罪將他起訴。北院審理時，黃男一改先前態度，與檢察官認罪協商，法官最後判罰3000元，得易服勞役3天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200610004118-260402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200610004118-260402&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=caa7e87c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200610004118-260402</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"《強暴美麗巨乳妹》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d16d36547f681a8a34bf9a318754e6765bc297","tid":2058642,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">易服</span>勞役3天</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da17e05136e9903e0fe0af6be2604be1f294434","tid":2058642,"uid":209073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XgEabPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgEabPs.gif&h=e7bbb66d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1538b98a7f78e2dea8225c634a2a948f3beb8d2","tid":2058642,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5798cd07e350cbaadff2adff124cf093f2047478","tid":2058642,"uid":103645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f6baf578ce970dd931f6bb70cce8752df91cbdd","tid":2058642,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">台北</span>市政府